args.code:
import pandas as pd

df = pd.read_csv('source_files/COMPAS.csv')

df['DateOfBirth'] = pd.to_datetime(df['DateOfBirth'])

df['Age'] = df['DateOfBirth'].apply(lambda x: 2024 - x.year)

df['Age'] = df['Age'].apply(lambda x: 1 if x > 30 else 0)

df['Sex_Code_Text'] = df['Sex_Code_Text'].apply(lambda x: 1 if x == 'Male' else 0)

protected_group_prob = df[df['Sex_Code_Text'] == 1]['Age'].mean()
non_protected_group_prob = df[df['Sex_Code_Text'] == 0]['Age'].mean()

risk_difference = protected_group_prob - non_protected_group_prob

print(risk_difference)
